languages.text: "Хротко, ты говорил, его еще не допрашивали. Почему на нем места живого нет?"
"I thought you said he was still waiting his turn. Why does he look beaten half to death?"

languages.text: «Tenía entendido que todavía esperaba su turno. ¿Por qué está medio muerto?».

languages.text: “你刚刚不是还说他在等候审讯吗？他怎么看起来被揍得半死不活？”
languages.original_text: "I thought you said he was still waiting his turn. Why does he look beaten half to death?"

languages.text: 「彼は、まだ順番待ち中だと言ってなかったか？何故、彼は半殺しになるまで殴られたように見えるんだ？」
languages.original_text: "I thought you said he was still waiting his turn. Why does he look beaten half to death?"

traits.locale_text: 「彼は、まだ順番待ち中だと言ってなかったか？何故、彼は半殺しになるまで殴られたように見えるんだ？」

languages.text: "Hattet Ihr nicht gesagt, er wäre noch nicht an der Reihe gewesen? Warum sieht er aus, als sei er halb totgeprügelt worden?"
languages.original_text: "I thought you said he was still waiting his turn. Why does he look beaten half to death?"

languages.text: "Hâlâ sırasını beklediğini söylediğini sanmıştım. Neden ölesiye dövülmüş gibi görünüyor?"
